        ∫_I |∑_{r=1}^R a_r e(ξ_r t)|^2 dt = (T + O(N)) ∑_{r=1}^R |a_r|^2.

  This file follows the user's handwritten proof, broken into Goals 1–7:

    Goal 1.  WLOG  ∑ |a_r|^2 = 1.
