             for ψ smooth, supported on [-1/4,1/4], ‖ψ‖_{L²} = 1.
    Goal 3.  (3.2) ∫_J |∑ a_r e(ξ_r t)|^2 dt ≪ N for any interval J of
             length N.
    Goal 4.  ∫_I |∑ a_r e(ξ_r t)|^2 dt
               = T - ∫_ℝ |∑ a_r e(ξ_r t)|^2 ( (1/N)∫_I |ψ̂((t-t₀)/N)|^2 dt₀
                                              - 1_I(t) ) dt.
